story.text: Danced the night away yestereve after a thrilling performance of Love's Labor's Lost by the Montana Shakespeare in the Parks. What an event and a talented crew. The dancing happened to [https://oldsaltunion.com/ Old Salt Union] - which was a fantastic string delight hailing from St. Louis. Which reminds me of the equally fantastic [http://peculiarpatriots.com/ Peculiar Patriots] that grooved last weekend.
I love live music like I love living.
